title: They See Me Trollblin
description: The tiny Kotassians hire the Warriors to exterminate two humongous Trollblins that have invaded their village, but it turns out that the Trollblins are actually nice guys and the Warriors switch sides to protect them in a Kotassiam/Trollblin War!

title: I……am Vampier
description: When Vic enters the Monte Macabre film festival, he gets insecure about his artistic vision and decides to copy the work of others, but ultimately learns that staying true to yourself is what's most important.

title: UG Christmas Special
description: Santa and Uncle Grandpa must work through their personal differences order to save Christmas.

title: Banana Joe
description: Cuando el director Brown le asigna a Darwin la tarea de hacer el anuario escolar, Darwin comienza pidiéndole a Banana Joe, el payaso de la clase, una simple selfi para la portada. Pero con Banana Joe, las cosas nunca son tan simples.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The Perfect Meal
description: KO teams up with Beardo to make the perfect meal for Carol.

title: #LosConejosMágicos
description: Cuando Zee le pide a Kara que cuide a sus dos conejitos mágicos, pronto comienzan a multiplicarse y a desatar el caos por toda Metrópolis.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Random Acts of Memory
description: The Warriors learn that Nohyas has been using a Selective Memory Magisword to erase select interactions with Prohyas' bizarre doppelganger their entire lives, so their new mission: take back that sword!

title: Te Quiero Mao Mao
description: Un solitario explosivo y su mejor amigo holgazán se desvían del viaje que los llevará a convertirse en leyenda y descubren que su historia apenas comienza.

title: Mr. Greg
description: Steven, Greg and Pearl take a trip to Empire City to live the good life.

title: Final Battle! Dan vs. Ajit/Secrets Exposed
description: Final Battle! Dan vs. Ajit: It's time for the event everyone in Los Volmos has been waiting for, The Bakugan Battle League finals! It's the Awesome Brawler's Dan Kouzo vs. the golden Bakugan brawler Ajit, these two face-off in a final brawl for it all./Secrets Exposed: The Bakugan Battle League has ended, and the winner has been determined, but the celebration is cut short when Phantom Thief Storm crashes the party by stealing everyone's Bakugan! It's up to Dan and Ajit to stop Storm and return all the stolen Bakugan.

title: Potencial Desperdiciado
description: A raíz de la victoria de la temporada anterior, los ninjas se han ablandado y el Maestro Wu debe recordarles quiénes son realmente.

title: Robo Teacher
description: When a substitute teacher fills in for Chef, Duncan thinks it's going to be the best day ever. He's wrong.

title: The Gilded Path
description: The headquarters to the resistance is breached and Lloyd scrambles to avoid capture. Meanwhile, the Ninja are caught by Heavy Metal, but find an unlikely ally.

title: Cowbar Jones: Origines
description: Pardo presenta la precuela de su película de Crowbar Jones a Nom Nom, con la esperanza de que acepte actuar en la película.

title: Classic Rock
description: Batman thinks he's helping a homeless old man who is being mugged on the street only to discover that the man is a powerful wizard being chased by demons in disguise. It turns out the wizard is on a mission to save Shazam from the clutches of Black Adam.

title: Three Gems and a Baby
description: Greg tells Steven the story of his first winter with Steven.

title: Sunken Treasure
description: A relaxing beach day becomes an underwater adventure when Unikitty and her friends find a message in a bottle.

title: A Rocky Start
description: The ninja have found their quest! Now they just have to get there, which involves a road trip through the Desert of Doom, a region supposedly inhabited by a giant scarab beetle.

title: Porque tan triste?
description: Steven ha escuchado rumores de un par de Gemas que todavía están destruyendo mundos. Si él no puede detenerlas, tal vez Lapis sí.

title: A Small Problem
description: When Ben is not allowed on an attraction at a water park because he to short, he decides to go alien to get even with the ride's attendant.

title: Burlate con Todas tus Fuerzas
description: Cuando Adorabat empieza a interrumpir agresivamente a todos con su nuevo poder que le da energía, se convierte en una amenaza para el reino entero.

title: Elect to Decline
description: Noville wants to impress Vambre with a new Magisword from the Cave of Stuff, but the Cave Weirdos are in election mode and horrible smear campaigning is making Noville's simple task impossible!

title: The More You Moe, the Moe You Know
description: Moe visits the tree house with a special birthday surprise for BMO. While BMO's mission stands on the brink of disaster, Finn & Jake host a strange guest.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Tiger Fail
description: Gwen refuses to be pressured into choosing an ice cream flavor that she does not want.

title: Lightfall Part 2
description: Lord Obsidian attacks the Lighthouse, but Mega Man overcomes his insecurity and works with his family to repel the big bad, who's rescued at the last second by a mysterious lieutenant, Namagem.

title: Anywhere but Sumo
description: When Clarence realizes Sumo has made a new group of friends at his new school, he becomes jealous and confused. Will Clarence accept a school life void of Sumo, or scheme his way into making their friendship work?

title: Tales from the Omnitrix
description: Team Tennyson trade campfire stories in an anthology-style series that pits Ben against his archrival, Kevin 11, and teaches our hero the power of imagination.

title: #TrianguloDeOdio
description: Cuando la exnovia de Hal aparece en el partido de bienvenida de la preparatoria Metrópolis y se enfurece por amor, convertida en la villana Star Sapphire, Jessica comienza a cuestionar sus propias tácticas no violentas.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Un Episodio Muy Especial
description: Cuarzo Arcoíris 2.0 prometió cuidar de Cebolla el mismo día que Heliolita programó una charla sobre la seguridad del hogar. ¿Es posible para Steven estar en dos lugares a la vez y ser dos fusiones al mismo tiempo?

title: La Explosion de Fuego Colosal
description: Cuando Colosal sale de un extraño estado de creatividad producto de una concentración extrema, es posible que haya hecho algo que podría destruir el Valle Puro Corazón entero.

title: Vreedlemania
description: Pa Vreedle reunites with Ma for all-out destruction.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Wild Wild Wheel Part 1
description: A dangerous lone gunslinger named WildWheel returns to Cybertron looking for Optimus Prime.

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: La Comida Perfecta
description: K.O. se alía a Beardo para prepararle la comida perfecta a Carol.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Gyranoide del Futuro
description: Manzana y Cebollín se esfuerzan por subir a la montaña rusa más loca del parque de diversiones.

title: For a Few Duncans More
description: While trying to photocopy his butt on Chef's fancy new copier Duncan accidentally makes an entire other Duncan. Great! This other Duncan can do all the school stuff while the real Duncan chills. But things go badly when the other Duncan decides to copy himself so he can chill too.

title: Snow Month
description: After a snow day saves Blossom from having to face a boy who's asked her out, she decides to use her ice breath to keep it going even if that means plunging Townsville into eternal winter complete with monstrous yetis!

title: Zing Your Heart Out
description: When Adorabat starts to aggressively heckle everyone with her new zing power, she threatens the entire kingdom.

title: Mutiny for the Bounty
description: While Phil and Grandpa Max tune-up the Omni-Copter, a restless Ben takes the Rustbuggy off road, but when he is suddenly captured by Textrax and the hunter takes the bounty for himself, our hero must not only escape but avoid the wrath of the double-crossed Kraab and Sixsix!

title: Dia de Elecciones
description: Manzana se presenta como candidato a alcalde.

title: The Best Friend/Thief and Brawler
description: The Best Friend: The top four brawlers in the Bakugan Battle League have been decided. For this round of the semi-finals it's a battle of best friends: Wynton vs. Dan. The winner of this battle between best buddies will move on to the championship round./Thief and Brawler: In the final battle of the Bakugan Battle league semi-finals it's Shun vs. Ajit. It's a grueling battle of focus, will, and strength, only a true brawler to emerge victorious.

title: The Belly of the Beast
description: To repair the Land-Bounty, the ninja must retrieve a critical engine component that has been swallowed by a giant scarab beetle.

title: 'Twas the Fight Before Christmas
description: When Princess Morbucks tries to ruin Christmas for the children of the world, the Powerpuff Girls must save the day.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: Chill Out
description: Uncle Grandpa takes a kid to the North Pole for an epic snowball battle.

title: Fideito
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben seguir teniendo la onda suficiente para aparecer en el video musical de su rapero favorito.

title: Strange Bedfellows
description: After an insane battle, MM and OS end up in the same hospital room. But even in full body casts, the sworn enemies continue the fight.

title: El Desnudo de Mao Mao
description: Cuando Mao Mao pierde la ropa mientras intenta escalar el Rubí Puro Corazón, tiene que regresar al cuartel general antes de que amanezca.

title: Buggy Out
description: After winning a Sumo Slammers Champion belt, Ben returns to the Rustbucket to find his prize in the arms of Kevin, but when his rival hijacks the Rustbuggy instead, our hero must stop at nothing to get back what's rightfully his!

title: Booby-Traps, and How To Survive Them
description: The ninja team up with a reluctant Clutch Powers to enter a mysterious pyramid where they inadvertently unleash an ancient evil.

title: El Vientre del Monstruo
description: Para reparar el Land-Bounty, el ninja debe recuperar un componente crítico del motor que ha sido tragado por un escarabajo gigante.

title: Duo Espinoso
description: Después de dejar Pequeña Escuela Madre, Steven ha encontrado un nuevo pasatiempo: las plantas.

title: No Day Like Snow Day
description: When a blizzard hits the town, Master Frown tries to ruin everyone's fun by pretending to be a magical snowman! But when he gets frozen inside, Master Frown must worry less about ruining everyone's good time and instead not turning into a Frown-sicle, while he's forced to experience the joys of the holiday season!

title: Bananas y Queso
description: Duncan está decidido a evitar que el dúo Banana y Queso se presente en la guardería.

title: The Christmas Special
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to destroy a gift for Santa to save Christmas.

title: Buscando Misiones
description: Al darse cuenta de que se han ablandado, el ninja busca una misión para reactivar su entrenamiento de Spinjitzu. Desafortunadamente, la ciudad de NINJAGO está disfrutando de un período de rara tranquilidad.

title: Lightfall Part 1
description: The mysterious Lord Obsidian calls Mega Man a traitor to robots and challenges him to a duel. An overconfident Mega Man is humbled by this mysterious new villain.

title: P.L.O.T. Device 2: Beyond the Bored Dome
description: Dr. Fox reprograms the P.L.O.T. Device to only generate boring events, but the gang can't help but add drama and excitement to every scenario.

title: The Boss
description: Gumball and Darwin help Rocky land an office job so that his dad, Mr. Robinson, will be proud of him. After a health scare the kids decide to reunite Mr Robinson with his son. Mr Robinson has always seen Rocky as a disappointment so when Gumball and Darwin help him land a corporate job at Chanax, he is thrilled. However the Chanax corporation is not quite what it seems. Can Gumball and Darwin rescue Rocky before he becomes a corporate drone for all eternity . . .

title: Un dia nevado
description: Cuando una tormenta de nieve llega a la ciudad, Master Frown trata de arruinar la diversión de todos fingiendo ser un muñeco de nieve mágico. Pero cuando se congela por dentro, Master Frown debe preocuparse menos por arruinar la diversión de todos y más por no convertirse en un témpano malhumorado, imientras se ve obligado a experimentar la alegría de la temporada navideña!

title: The Director/Queen Ebony
description: The Director: Everett Ray reaches out to Lia with an opportunity that seems too good to be true. Everett is now working in show business and proposes to make Lia's dream of becoming a film director come true. He's taken care of all the arrangements; all Lia has to do is provide the directorial vision./Queen Ebony: On his daily jaunt, Lightning learns of a street cat named Ebony, who's been treating dogs like servants, threatening them to do her bidding or face the wrath of her Bakugan! Lightning tries to reason with Ebony but when that doesn't work, it turns into a cat vs. dog Bakugan brawl!

title: CarolQuest
description: Carol is forced to bring KO along as she defends the Plaza from a new threat.

title: Holly Jolly Secrets Part 2
description: Finn and Jake continue to explore the world of old Christmas specials while the Ice King fumes.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Perfect Tree
description: Chloe and Ice Bear drive up north to find the perfect Christmas tree. Meanwhile, Grizz and Panda are in charge of decorating Chloe's house.

title: Merry Christmas Mordecai
description: Mordecai has to get through a Christmas party with C.J. without messing everything up.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Presentando a Kevin 11
description: En un encuentro de intercambio local, Ben se interesa en un coleccionable de Luchadores de Sumo. Pero cuando Kevin se apodera del objeto, nuestro héroe debe superar el arma secreta de Kevin para recuperarlo: iun 11º extraterrestre!

title: El Arbol Perfecto
description: Chloe y Polar conducen hacia el norte para encontrar el árbol de Navidad perfecto. Mientras tanto, Pardo y Panda quedan a cargo de la decoración de la casa de Chloe.

title: Christmas Parties
description: The Bears have been invited to all their friends' Christmas parties. In an effort to have time to crash Nom Nom's huge star-studded bash, the Bears first try to make quick stops at all their friends' parties throughout the night.

title: Trampas y Como Sobrevivir a Ellas
description: El ninja se une a un clutch Powers renuente para entrar en una misteriosa pirámide donde desatan sin darse cuenta un antiguo mal.

title: Little Graduation
description: Steven and the Gems celebrate Little Homeschool's first graduating class.

title: Hideous Hound
description: Prohyas pets an unsightly stray dog, and from that moment on the poor pooch appears on a variety of Warrior missions, driving Vambre and Vambre's brain insane!

title: Rush to Greatness
description: Rush puts his new battle upgrades to the test in a battle with Wave Man.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Plaza Abandonada
description: Es el cumpleaños de KO, y Rad y Enid quieren asegurarse de que todo salga a la perfección.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: La Dinamica del Dinamo
description: iAxel se encuentra en el centro de un desacuerdo entre Sarge y Masko sobre lo que es más importante en la batalla, el arma o el que lo maneja, después de que Dynamo une al trío!

title: Plaza Alone
description: It's KO's birthday, and Rad and Enid want to make sure everything goes perfectly.

title: Thunderhowl Part 1
description: Bumblebee and Chromia travel to Crystal City to recover one of Windblade's psychic shards and encounter a long-lost bot.

title: Manzana, Concentrate
description: Manzana ayuda a Cebollín a cumplir su sueño de competir en un programa de pastelería.

title: Why So Blue?
description: Steven has heard rumors of a pair of Gems that are still destroying worlds. If he can't stop them, maybe Lapis can.

title: The Gift
description: The girls must replace the Professor's Christmas present on Christmas Eve.

title: El castigo de mi vida
description: Owen forma un nexo especial con Duncan después de que ambos se divirtieran mucho durante sus castigos.

title: Swish
description: Namagem attacks Mega Man using a variety of powers, revealing that they both can replicate schematics. However, Namagem can carry more than three at a time! The true beginning of the mysterious villain's arc begins here.

title: Firstbourne
description: Emperor Garmadon has taken control of Ninjago City where Lloyd retreats to the shadows. Meanwhile, the other Ninja and Young Wu are shipwrecked in the Realm of Oni & Dragon and find they are not alone.

title: El Oso
description: In a flashback to long ago, Charlie has an adventure in the Mexican desert.

title: Night of the Bat
description: Superman and other Justice League members have to battle Batman when he gets possessed by an evil Djinn, Uthool, who is intent on using the JL power core to blow a crack in Earth.

title: Secret Santa
description: When Uncle Grandpa and the crew all have the same popular and hard-to-find gift in mine for their Secret Santa, their nice Christmas shopping trip to the mall turns into a crazy competition.

title: Christmas in Space
description: The guys celebrate their first Christmas in space by opening presents, eating peppermint bark and telling Christmas stories. Benson wants the stories to be more Christmas-y but the guys keep adding scary elements, which only infuriate their boss.

title: La Mision de Carol
description: Carol se ve obligada a llevar a KO con ella mientras defiende la Plaza de una nueva amenaza.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Return of the Honeysuckle Rangers
description: Craig discovers that the Honeysuckle Rangers have snuck into his side of the Creek to steal his most prized possession.

title: Merry Christmas
description: When the Rustbucket's A/C goes on the fritz in the middle of the desert, Ben, Max and Gwen take refuge at Holiday Village, an over the top Christmas theme park that seems to appear out of nowhere. The place is run by an evil entity known as Mr. Jingles, who takes Max prisoner because he believes Max is Santa! It's up to Ben and Gwen to free Max and break the spell Mr. Jingles has cast on Holiday Village, freeing others who've been trapped their for years and releasing the theme park.

title: Holly Jolly Secrets Part 1
description: Finn and Jake continue to explore the world of old Christmas specials while the Ice King fumes.

title: Lista de Traviesos
description: Es Nochebuena y Brock está emocionado por la visita de Santa Claus. Mientras se prepara para que Master Frown le lea un cuento para dormir, Unikitty y la banda irrumpen en su casa. Están ahí para evitar que Master Frown arruine más Navidades. Frown se declara inocente, pero Unikitty y la banda cuentan las historias de las Navidades pasadas que ya arruinó. ¿Frown probará su inocencia o se pondrá a la cabeza de la lista de los traviesos?

title: Victor the Predictor
description: When Victor becomes convinced he has a special talent as a psychic, he decides to use his new mental abilities to counsel those around him - until one piece of advice goes too far.

title: Pony Tale
description: Uncle Grandpa grows a ponytail, which gains him the attention of a magical pony.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Meet Tygra
description: The smartest Thundercat, Tygra. Tygra's mission is to make Lion-O a better leader. He might get around to it too, if he wasn't so busy cleaning up after the other Thundercats.

title: Hip hip Hurra
description: Bridgette tiene hipo y está desesperada por librarse de ellos.

title: Temple of Mars
description: Searching for answers on Mars, Finn and Jermaine discover that they must first survive a cunning Martian mental trap.

title: Memories of Bobby
description: When a pillar of the Creek community leaves, our trio mourns their loss by remembering the good times.

title: La Aventura Perfecta
description: Cuando a Mao Mao se le antoja vivir la aventura perfecta, Adorabat dice una mentira piadosa.

title: Radio Ninjago libre
description: Lloyd deberá encontrar su voz mientras lidera una pequeña resistencia para capturar las señales de transmisión en Ciudad Ninjago. Mientras tanto en el Primer Reino, el Barón de Hierro lleva a los Ninjas en una cacería de dragones.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Los Jovenes Titanes Salvan la Navidad
description: Santa renuncia a la Navidad, y los Titanes deben intervenir para salvar la festividad.

title: Attack of Thermometron 9000
description: Axel must wrangle Galileo and Bobbie to shut down a rogue thermostat - improperly upgraded by Slobot - as it plunges the house into extreme hot and cold zones.

title: Una ninja justicia para Harold
description: El mundo de Harold queda de cabeza cuando sus compañeros declaran que Beth es la verdadera ninja de la clase.

title: Bananas & Cheese
description: Duncan is determined to stop the musical duo Bananas & Cheese from coming to the daycare.

title: Aventuras Cuidando Ninos
description: Ben, Gwen y Max se encuentran con una familia que parece ser un reflejo de ellos. Pero cuando Max sale a caminar con su matriarca, Maxine, Ben se ve obligado a cuidar a Simon Sez, un malcriado con una mochila diseñada por Billy Billones, que lo convierte en un robot formidable.

title: El Oso
description: En flashes retrospectivos al pasado lejano, vemos una aventura de Charlie en el desierto mexicano.

title: Paseo en Buggy
description: Después de ganar un cinturón como campeón de Luchadores de Sumo, Ben regresa al Rustbucket y encuentra su premio en los brazos de Kevin. Pero cuando su rival secuestra el Rustbuggy, inuestro héroe no debe detenerse ante nada para recuperar lo que le pertenece legítimamente!

title: Abate and Switch
description: When the JLA tries to stop the Brothers Djinn, the ghoulish trio are able to direct spells on our heroes by saying their names forcing them to disguise themselves as each other in order to foil the spells.

title: Halloween vs. Navidad
description: Cuando Santa Claus intenta apoderarse de Halloween, los Titanes necesitan a un par de espíritus para detenerlo.

title: Steven Floats
description: Steven is so excited to be back home that he jumps for joy and jumps way too high.

title: Lil Noodle
description: Apple and Onion must remain legit enough to be in their favorite rapper's music video.

title: Rook Tales
description: Rook's former teacher will preserve Revonnahgander traditions at any cost.

title: Winter Forecast
description: Steven has to get Connie home before it snows.

title: Top of the Naughty List
description: It's Christmas Eve and Brock is excited for Santa to come and visit as he settles down for a bedtime story from Master Frown, Unikitty and gang burst in. They are there to stop Master Frown from ruining any more Christmases. Frown pleads innocent but Unikitty and the gang tell the stories of the past Christmases he has already ruined.  Will Frown prove his innocence or will he rocket to the top of the Naughty List?

title: Here Comes Haavik/The Fusion Bakugan Arrive
description: Here Comes Haavik: An evil shapeshifting alien has landed in Los Volmos! If that wasn't bad enough, he has a group of robot mechanoids on his trail trying to bring him justice. Meanwhile, Dan has accepted a battle challenge from a pair of brawlers, Chad and Trey./The Fusion Bakugan Arrive: Still humiliated by their defeat, Chad and Trey challenge Dan to rematch but this time they have a few tricks up their sleeve, and a little help on their side.

title: Election Day
description: Apple runs for Mayor.

title: The Ballad of Mr. Baumann
description: The grouchy storekeeper has a big secret, and she's not of this Earth.

title: Teen Titans Save Christmas
description: Santa calls it quits so the Titans must pitch in to save the holiday.

title: Cuatro por Cuatro
description: Durante su visita a Ciudad Gemelos, Ben y Gwen se inscriben en una competencia de laser-tag. Pero cuando Ben se une a Kevin, los dos deben superar sus diferencias si quieren terminar en la cima.

title: Drop Beat Dad
description: Steven helps Sour Cream put on a show, even though Sour Cream's stepdad doesn't approve of DJs.

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: #FantasticBeastsAndHowToMindThem
description: Diana Prince receives a care package from home, and her pet-raising skills are soon put to the test when a mysterious egg hatches into a baby griffin.

title: Companeros de Cama Extranos
description: Tras una batalla demencial, Mao Mao y Cobrangután terminan internados en la misma habitación de hospital. Pero incluso con yesos que les cubren todo el cuerpo, los enemigos declarados siguen peleando.

title: Questing For Quests
description: Realizing they have gone soft, the ninja search for a quest to reignite their Spinjitzu training. Unfortunately, NINJAGO City is enjoying a period of rare tranquility.

title: Merry Moochmas
description: It's wintertime in Aberdale and Clarence is convinced his winter wish for snow in Arizona will come true! However, his classmate Belson along with his grumpy cousin Gary Mooch are a little tougher to convince.

title: Jacob del Arroyo
description: Un terrible corte de cabello obliga a Craig a visitar el Arroyo de encubierto.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Huelga por el Botin
description: Mientras Phil y el abuelo Max afinan el Omni-Copter, Ben, inquieto, saca el Rustbuggy de la carretera. Pero cuando de repente es capturado por Tetrax, nuestro héroe no solo debe escapar, sino también evitar la ira de los traicioneros Kraab y SeiSeis.

title: Sophie, the Bakuganist/Midnight Train Battle!
description: Sophie, the Bakuganist: Magnus is on the trail of the illegal Baku-brawling devices and, is looking to cut off the supply at its source. When he witnesses an illegal deal going down, he knows it's up to him to go after the shipment to keep the illegal devices off the street./Midnight Train Battle!: Sophie Judson Warfield, a wealthy activist with the Citizens to Save Bakugan Society, is working to put an end to all Bakugan brawling. Her latest target is the Awesome Brawlers themselves. When Wynton doesn't take Sophie seriously, the encounter quickly turns into an all-out Bakugan brawl.

title: Lucky Girl
description: Ben battles an evil sorcerer whose power whose emanates from mystic charms, one of which turns Gwen into her own superhero named Lucky Girl.

title: The Dynamo Dynamic
description: Axel finds himself at the center of a disagreement between Sarge and Masko over what's more important in battle - the weapon or the one who wields it - after Dynamo bonds the trio together!

title: Christmas Movies
description: On Christmas Eve, the Baby Bears defend a video store from getting robbed.

title: El Regreso de los Guardabosques Madreselva
description: Craig descubre que los Guardabosques Madreselva se han infiltrado en su lado del Arroyo para robar su posesión más preciada.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Snow Tubing
description: Rigby wants Eileen to go snow tubing.

title: How to Build a Dragon
description: While Lloyd and the rebels celebrate their successful strike against Emperor Garmadon, in the Realm of Oni and Dragon, the Ninja dare an elaborate escape from the clutches of Iron Baron and his Dragon Hunters.

title: The Chupaca-bro
